===Etymology 1===
Originally an [[acronym]] of the expression: {{term||[[wonder]] [[of]] [[wonders]]}}.

====Interjection====
{{en-intj}}

# An indication of [[excitement]] or [[surprise]].
#: '''''Wow!''' I never expected this!''
# An expression of [[amazement]] or [[awe]].
#: '''''Wow!''' How do they do that?''

